    Type in a new memo:
    <br/>
    <textarea name="text" cols="80" rows="15"></textarea>
  </p>
  <p>
    or <a href="/memo/file">upload from a file</a>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    email addresses to send to (separate by commas):
  </p>
